  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Cook pasta according to package instructions until al dente. Drain and set aside.",
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat. Add garlic and red pepper, sauté for about 2 minutes or until fragrant.",
    "Add cumin and smoked paprika, cook for another minute.",
    "Stir in black beans, vegetable broth, nutritional yeast, lemon juice, salt, and pepper. Bring to a simmer.",
    "Fold cooked pasta into the sauce, cooking over medium-low heat until heated through, about 5 minutes.",
    "Serve hot."
